The paper deals with radio resource management in vehicular networks, which is a subfield of computer networking (cs.NI). The proposed algorithm is based on deep reinforcement learning techniques (cs.LG, cs.AI) and involves decision-making under uncertainty (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the modeling of the problem as a Markov decision process (cs.IT).
